parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the forward collision avoidance system can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop or brake without warning, which can lead to accidents or injuries. Additionally, the system's failure to function properly can compromise the safety of the vehicle's occupants and other road users.
symptoms: The forward collision avoidance warning light illuminates
the vehicle suddenly stops or brakes without warning
the seat belt tightens independently
the system randomly engages while making a turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts for the recall repair can cause a delay in fixing the forward collision avoidance system, leaving the vehicle's occupants and other road users at risk.
symptoms: The part to do the recall repair is unavailable
the manufacturer exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
the contact had not experienced a failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sunroof and Rear View Window Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof or rear view window can cause distractions, injuries, and accidents.
symptoms: Loud bang
wind noise
and shattered glass; sunshade in the rear view window breaking and staying in the up position
obstructing visibility.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning PCS can cause false warnings, sudden braking, and accidents.
symptoms: False collision warnings
sudden braking
and activation of the brake lights; PCS misreading objects on the road
causing unnecessary warnings and braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden acceleration
high RPMs
and difficulty stopping the vehicle; coasting forward with light brake pressure
and sudden acceleration when pulling into a parking space.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of interior trim and mirrors can cause distractions, injuries, and accidents.
symptoms: Rear headliner detaching from the interior roof
compromising rear visibility; passenger side mirror exploding and shattering
potentially causing injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning air conditioning system can cause discomfort, health issues, and distractions.
symptoms: Musty
urine-type smell when turning on the air conditioner; foul odor causing headaches and discomfort.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The reflection of sunlight from the dashboard chrome trim can cause temporary blindness, distractions, and accidents.
symptoms: Bright work on the dash reflecting sunlight into the driver's eyes
causing temporary blindness.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the pre-collision system can cause the vehicle to brake suddenly or incorrectly, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The pre-collision system warning light comes on
the vehicle brakes suddenly
the seatbelts tighten
and the vehicle decelerates without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning blower switch/motor can cause the air conditioner to malfunction, leading to discomfort and potential health issues.
symptoms: The air conditioner blows hot air when the car is stopped
the air conditioner works only when the car is moving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door actuators can cause the doors to not lock or unlock properly, leading to safety and security issues.
symptoms: The doors do not lock or unlock
the doors do not respond to the key fob.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system malfunctions
the battery drains
the car won't start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The center console heat issue can cause discomfort and potential burns.
symptoms: The center console becomes extremely hot to the touch
a burning odor is present inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions and discomfort.
symptoms: The door panel rattles
the Bluetooth works inconsistently
the information center becomes blank.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine fire can cause serious accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Smoke appears from under the hood
the front of the vehicle catches fire.
